Ofgem Hires BDO to Scrutinize ‘Big Six’ Profits, Telegraph Says

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-08-21T07:09:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/ofgem-hires-bdo-to-scrutinize-big-six-profits-telegraph-says.html
U.K. energy regulator  Ofgem  hired
accountants from BDO International to examine how the country’s
so-called Big Six energy companies calculate their profits, the
Sunday Telegraph reported, citing an Ofgem spokesman it didn’t
identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in  London  
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net . 